<style>
	#leftmain {
	  border-right:none; 
	}
	h2 {border:none; }
</style>

<div class="container">
  <p>Develop your application with the 10gen <a href="/wiki/SDK">SDK</a> and then deploy it to the cloud.<br />10gen cloud usage is free for the alpha, and 
